Maafkan aku.

709
01:16:28,047 --> 01:16:29,757
Aku juga.

710
01:16:34,012 --> 01:16:35,388
Perintah berubah!

711
01:16:35,472 --> 01:16:38,266
Lindungi Aeon, lindungi Goodchild!

712
01:17:19,891 --> 01:17:21,601
Goodchild tertembak!

713
01:17:25,605 --> 01:17:27,440
Flux sedang menuju halaman!

714
01:17:31,194 --> 01:17:32,779
Lindungi Aeon!

715
01:18:56,530 --> 01:18:57,698
Sithandra!

716
01:19:49,000 --> 01:19:50,960
Oren.

717
01:20:23,785 --> 01:20:25,703
Mereka datang.

718
01:20:30,583 --> 01:20:32,460
Aeon...

719
01:20:51,688 --> 01:20:54,232
Kami menunggu perintahmu.

720
01:20:54,315 --> 01:20:57,277
Kalian bukan bagian dari ini?

721
01:20:57,360 --> 01:21:00,321
Apa pun kami,
kami bukan kaum anarkis.

722
01:21:00,405 --> 01:21:03,199
- Harus ada peraturan.
- Terima kasih.

723
01:21:34,981 --> 01:21:37,108
Kaulah orangnya.

724
01:21:37,192 --> 01:21:39,110
Kau menyelamatkanku.

725
01:21:39,194 --> 01:21:41,488
Benar.

726
01:21:41,571 --> 01:21:43,323
Aku mengenalmu saat itu.

727
01:21:43,406 --> 01:21:46,368
Yang satu ini rusak.
Hancurkan saja.

728
01:21:46,451 --> 01:21:49,120
Aku tahu kau penting.

729
01:21:49,204 --> 01:21:50,830
DNA-nya masih bagus.

730
01:21:50,914 --> 01:21:52,916
Hancurkan.

731
01:21:58,129 --> 01:22:01,424
Aku tahu bahwa aku
harus melindungimu.

732
01:22:02,509 --> 01:22:07,180
Aku menyembunyikan DNA-mu di sini
dalam kondisi dorman.

733
01:22:07,264 --> 01:22:10,141
